{"tid":128453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖意外　機車騎士下巴遭鐵欄圍籬刺入","createTime":"2017-02-20T23:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T01:03:08.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54ddbdca39c86729e8160ee258b8479c60887afe","tid":128453,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:45:04.000Z","msg":"印度一名男子以高速騎著機車，他撞到減速帶失控，凌空飛撲向前，並撞到金屬圍籬欄杆，欄杆尖端刺穿他的下巴並從他的口中冒出，場面極為恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生在當地時間上周三(15日)，目擊者指出，20歲男子坎特(Bhavnalo Kant)騎著機車以高速行駛，「他沒看到路上突起的減速壆(路面為了讓車輛減速所鋪設的突起物)，機車撞到後失控，他凌空撲向前，下巴撞上欄杆的尖端」。<br />\n<br />\n坎特的同車乘客被摔落地，見他受傷立即跑到警局尋求協助。從影片可見，至少4人上前協助坎特，將他移離欄杆，他當時神情呆滯，傷口不斷冒血。最後坎特由救護車送院做手術，幸好手術成功，現時已脫離危險期。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170220/420_f9ce4837819ddbd9ddab3421b6802b57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170220%2F420_f9ce4837819ddbd9ddab3421b6802b57.jpg&h=5b9a251e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坎特的下巴直接插上圍籬尖端的刺。翻攝自《鏡報》<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170220/420_f83e26bc08cb9675ec57642955eb7a9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170220%2F420_f83e26bc08cb9675ec57642955eb7a9c.jpg&h=646d6ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自《鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170220/1060256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170220%2F1060256%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=85528736\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170220/1060256/</a>"},{"pid":"2537f82148103a48d14ef5e5ab34d5db9cedd530","tid":128453,"uid":4286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T00:07:00.000Z","msg":"發明減速壆出黎嘅人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji